Pax Angaia

	Philosophy

		-
			Pax Angaia refers to the growth of Angaianism as a unifying force by way of the
			universal applicability and non-falsifiability of its core tenets.
		-

	Principles

		Angaian Amalgamation

			-
				Any philosophy or institution can be said to be Angaianist to the extent that its
				principles overlap with Angaianism, and its spread or growth can be said to serve
				the ends of pax Angaia to said extent.
			-